{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904730/extras/Welcome_to_Custom_Party.gif?t=1728923343\" /><br><br><strong>Custom Party, the free indie online party game based on customization !</strong><br><br>Custom Party is a <strong>party game for 2 to 8 players</strong> <strong>online</strong>.<br>It contains a <strong>unique customization system</strong> and <strong>lots of mini-games</strong> to play !<br><br><strong>Which makes this game a great experience to play with friends or even in competition!</strong><br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904730/extras/Customize_your_character.gif?t=1728923343\" /><br><br><strong>All elements of customization for your character are essential ! </strong><br><br>Choose your <strong>hats, shoes, tops, and colors</strong> wisely! All items affect <strong>your playstyle</strong> by <strong>changing stats</strong> or even <strong>powers</strong> !<br><strong>Combined with the fact that it is a multiplayer game, this gives each playthrough a unique experience !</strong><br><br><i>All hats, tops, bottoms and colors will not be paid for, all items are completely free.</i><br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904730/extras/Take_a_risk.gif?t=1728923343\" /><br><br><strong>We are introducing an innovative new ranking system called \u00ab Take A Risk !\u00a0\u00bb !</strong><br><br>It works by choosing a number of <strong>Ranking Points</strong> that you must stake in each game you play !<br>So this gives players who feel underranked <strong>a chance to face</strong> higher ranked players by <strong>taking a risk</strong> !<br><br>Additionally, it encourages cautious players to bet less, and slowly but surely progress to <strong>new ranks</strong> !<br><br><strong>Everyone can play however they want !</strong>","backgro